{"tid":1912531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔19歲男生連儂牆派傳單遭劏肚致腸外溢   中国籍廚師或被改控企圖謀殺","createTime":"2020-03-06T06:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T15:03:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce348867529830fbef6de7fb28f45a7a0a54ad0","tid":1912531,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200306/_2020030612564485845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200306%2F_2020030612564485845.jpg&h=3e128e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22歲被告柳国升(小圖)<br />\n<br />\n去年10月港鐵大埔墟站外「連儂牆」附近，19歲男子在站外派發呼籲民眾遊行傳單時，遭內地漢先以生果刀刺傷頸背，再遭刺傷左腹部，身受重傷。內地漢事後到警署自首，被控一項有意圖而傷人罪。他一直還柙，今在高等法院申請保釋被拒，續須還柙看管。據了解，被告或會被改控一項企圖謀殺罪。<br />\n<br />\n22歲被告柳国升，報稱任職廚師，報稱住址為廣西博白鎮，持雙程證來港。控罪指，他於去年10月19日在新界大埔雅運路近港鐵大埔墟站入口，意圖使熊姓男子身體受嚴重傷害，而非法及惡意傷害該名男子。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1716606/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%9419%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E9%81%AD%E5%8A%8F%E8%82%9A%E8%87%B4%E8%85%B8%E5%A4%96%E6%BA%A2-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%BB%9A%E5%B8%AB%E6%88%96%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%B9%E6%8E%A7%E4%BC%81%E5%9C%96%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0127366b8b7ee0a6da0f8021618e6778c90e9bc8","tid":1912531,"uid":213877,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:50:56.000Z","msg":"中国籍廚師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉去打靶啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf1c44f37313014ae33d9e47b92409ff71d4642","tid":1912531,"uid":177213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:51:00.000Z","msg":"喺香港啜足一世資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces